’Щ@cbcaa3c7d113c2cdd3a40e015aef0e03aab2899254751cec54f6a548278d18c7Щ·Title: title: ansi link
Path: Flags
Content:
``--text, -t {string}``
: Link text. Uses uri as text if absent. In case of

tables, records and lists applies this text to all elements.
’Щ@59c8312cb23638a9b5bce3d0838e1c9162b60ec88d3957372e4e7f844ff8c07aЩЋTitle: title: ansi link
Path: Parameters
Content:
``...rest``
: For a data structure input, add links to all strings at the given cell paths.
